    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver that's ready for its next adventure? This car is in fair condition and offers a fantastic opportunity for anyone seeking a reliable ride at a great value! It has plenty of life left and is perfect for getting you where you need to go with confidence and style.",
